# Bilingual Slovak-Slovene Word Representations

This repository contains the code and evaluation data for the project.

The implementation is based on the hyperwords project. Learn more at: https://bitbucket.org/omerlevy/hyperwords

Parts of the code are reused from:
"A Strong Baseline for Learning Cross-Lingual Word Embeddings from Sentence Alignments"
Omer Levy, Anders SÃ¸gaard, and Yoav Goldberg. EACL 2017.
https://bitbucket.org/omerlevy/xling_embeddings
